%% E091 - Simulated auth flow sequence - F1-9 API Auth
%% Source: docs/design/f1-9-auth.md (E090)
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant SPA
    participant API as AuthController
    participant JWT as JWT Service

    Note over User,JWT: Login
    User->>SPA: Enter email/password
    SPA->>API: POST /api/auth/login {email, password}
    API->>JWT: GenerateToken(sub, email, role: admin)
    JWT-->>API: JWT string
    API-->>SPA: 200 {token, expiresAt, user}
    SPA->>SPA: Store token (localStorage/memory)

    Note over User,JWT: Protected request
    User->>SPA: Navigate /buscar (or any route)
    SPA->>API: GET /api/rulings/search Authorization: Bearer {token}
    API->>API: Validate JWT (issuer, audience, signature)
    alt Token valid
        API-->>SPA: 200 OK (response)
    else Token invalid or missing
        API-->>SPA: 401 Unauthorized (ProblemDetails)
    end
